24 PRESIDENTIAL CANDIDATE, I AGREE TO SERVE AND TO MARK MY BALLOTS FOR THAT
25 CANDIDATE AND FOR THAT CANDIDATE’S VICE PRESIDENTIAL RUNNING MATE.”.
26 (C) THE EXECUTED PLEDGES SHALL ACCOMPANY THE SUBMISSION OF THE
