31 AS A CANDIDATE FOR THAT OFFICE IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE RULES OF THE
32 POLITICAL PARTY, THE PLEDGE EXECUTED UNDER SUBSECTION (A) OF THIS
33 SECTION OR § 8–507(D) OF THIS SUBTITLE APPLIES TO THE SUCCESSOR CANDIDATE
34 FOR THAT OFFICE NOMINATED BY THE POLITICAL PARTY IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE
35 PARTY RULES.

